know how to get into the load position and

00:03:56.605 --> 00:04:02.435
you don’t know how to build power out of
it which is the next component, then this

00:04:02.435 --> 00:04:06.295
position serves no purpose.

00:04:06.295 --> 00:04:15.435
This is like putting the cart before the horse,
you’re not focusing on the foundation which

00:04:15.435 --> 00:04:24.725
is this component into the power component
